    "description": "来自获奖游戏《Prison Boss VR》的开发者现将进军PC VR领域，为大家带来《Winds &amp; Leaves》。<br><br>你被困在一片贫瘠的土地之上，是唯一掌握着古老的植物种植之术之人。世界无比脆弱，你必须想办法解决威胁世界的众多灾难。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种植自己的森林</h2>从无到有，创造不同的树种来适应不同的生物群落和气候。日积月累，将贫瘠的土地变成郁郁葱葱的山谷。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/2ad26c75b562b74f3ce5c77320ee294a.poster.avif?t=1746736289\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/2ad26c75b562b74f3ce5c77320ee294a.webm?t=1746736289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/2ad26c75b562b74f3ce5c77320ee294a.mp4?t=1746736289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开世界的秘密</h2>在高跷上探索一个趣味横生且不断变化的世界，这是专门为穿越各色景观、攀爬阴翳树林而设计的运动系统。寻觅古老建筑，唤醒它们来发现其中的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/3418b666be8192520de8f9aa72d08ab4.poster.avif?t=1746736289\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/3418b666be8192520de8f9aa72d08ab4.webm?t=1746736289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/3418b666be8192520de8f9aa72d08ab4.mp4?t=1746736289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感受生机勃勃的自然</h2>享受来自Vibe Avenue的世界获奖作曲家们带来的配乐，它们不断变化、还能对你周围的世界作出反应；同时见证荒芜地貌逐渐转变为绿意盎然的森林。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/15fa34c87d16dbca73db36024f6f7fe8.poster.avif?t=1746736289\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/15fa34c87d16dbca73db36024f6f7fe8.webm?t=1746736289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783750/extras/15fa34c87d16dbca73db36024f6f7fe8.mp4?t=1746736289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
